----------------------------------------------------( Conclusion )---------------------------------------------------------
In the nut-shell, AI has very important impact in testing tools and in test automation of application program. With out the Artifical intelligent it take
a lot of time and even more difficulty in exectution of the test scenarios but with the use of this third layer in test automation it improve accuracy,
give better test converage,saves our lot of time and moeny,quickly insights the test results and also stable test automation.Many new features are
also being added in test automation of applications.




